ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 243, Yukon
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 243 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to the YUKON with respect to the spring flooding that occurred from June 24 to September 23, 2021.
